source: crates/tk/tests/scenarios.rs
expression: "p.run(&format!(\"{command} --help\"))"
---
Select the next ready Ticket

Usage: tk next [EPIC_ID]

Arguments:
  [EPIC_ID]  Restrict selection to this Epic's child Tickets. Falls back to the `TK_SCOPE` environment variable; absent both, all ready Tickets are considered

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
